Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【Main】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1311,885)\fad(500,500)\fs90\bord4}方修利的決意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督 真的什麼都沒發生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.19,0:01:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為宿醉 腦子裡嗡嗡響
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.57,0:01:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喝了這麼多？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.53,0:01:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後一直喝到天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}路易·艾德蒙·巴傑斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ルイ・エドモン・パジェス
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:01:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.90,0:02:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人真的乾喝到天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:02:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(552,923)\fad(500,500)}米哈伊爾·瓦倫科夫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:02:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(552,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ミハエル・ワレンコフ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是昨晚的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(845,923)\fad(500,500)}方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(845,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ファン・ヒューリック
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿醉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 我辛苦做的豈不是白費了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我問過了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要我為他做點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就答道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃蛋包飯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想什麼呢 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的外號是提督啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之謝謝妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.80,0:02:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要細細品味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們賓館還真是服務周到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我來的時候也要拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡已經要關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.71,0:02:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩晚上一份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的日子也更不好過了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要關門呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:02:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想改造成大廳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝潢保證豪華
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他 買下了這裡要蓋大廈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞真讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也真辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能找別的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個星球不怎麼景氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,材料不足 人手也不足
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缺東少西的 不知什麼時候才能整備完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有錢就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒錢才頭疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}李博士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ドクター・リー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有比這裡更便宜的工廠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利提督正做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}米蘭達·卡西米爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ミランダ・カジミール
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在閒晃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像沒什麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還真悠閒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士想讓提督和泰坦尼亞作對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想親眼目睹歷史的變革
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然找到了觀測對象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對方卻不買我的帳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他太超脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他若能對泰坦尼亞感到憤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就容易煽動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憤怒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是私事也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能激起他的怒火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會成為變革的導火索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若提督不動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能說明時機尚未成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機一旦成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運之輪自會開始運轉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}艾曼塔 亞瑟斯·泰坦尼亞伯爵府
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エーメンタール アルセス・タイタニア伯爵邸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(635,923)\fad(500,500)}亞瑟斯·泰坦尼亞伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(635,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}アルセス・タイタニア伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殘酷之中自有美的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不這樣認為嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不想去理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你殺了奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(485,923)\fad(500,500)}莉拉·佛羅倫茲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(485,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}リラ・フローレンツ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修連的女人性子好烈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修連？你說誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我注意點態度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯閣下來電
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就當好妳的誘餌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督 我們這樣無所事事好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 又沒什麼事情做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船的整備一完成 就馬上出航嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒決定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒決定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督 你真想就這樣做個走私商嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有公開處刑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？艾曼塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 這不是個女人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女人犯什麼罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但泰坦尼亞這次還真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(945,923)\fad(500,500)}「正直老人」號
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(945,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}「正直じいさん」号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉那件事是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是那個亞瑟斯伯爵搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅是米蘭達的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我的途徑也得到了同樣的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方故意將此事公諸於世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用了「處刑」這種刺激的字眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方的目的很明顯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒辦法救她了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣無疑是自尋死路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唰地潛入進去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪回莉拉馬上逃離…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞絕非善類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情想都不要想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉… 提督的女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方正嚴陣以待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若貿然前去 只會正中對方下懷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你還堅持要去的話 我不反對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要行動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞的天敵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真頭疼 哲力胥卿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道唆使亞瑟斯的就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1154,923)\fad(500,500)}伊德里斯·泰坦尼亞公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1154,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}イドリス・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是和他談過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:08:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}哲力胥·泰坦尼亞公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:08:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ザーリッシュ・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:07:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然抓女人做人質
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是泰坦尼亞的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在全宇宙人面前出醜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你如何向殿下交代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不用交代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此事是亞瑟斯的獨斷獨行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和您無關
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥卿還真疼愛弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.53,0:08:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此事我早晚要問個清楚 伊德里斯卿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,803)\fad(500,500)\fs40}Uraniberg
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,878)\fad(500,500)}天城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,918)\fad(500,500)\fs31\fnms gothic}ウラニボルグ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,988)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}天の城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟斯伯也真讓人頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點老套
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但挾持人質乃是兵法之常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但居然要公開處刑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戲演得太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(621,923)\fad(500,500)}褚士朗·泰坦尼亞公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(621,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ジュスラン・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很卑劣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但此計牽涉甚廣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕不是亞瑟斯自己的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯卿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利想必也知道這是個陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說應該會無視吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1284,863)\fad(500,500)}亞歷亞伯特·泰坦尼亞公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1284,933)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}アリアバート・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣一來 他就會成為負心漢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為天下人所唾棄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若貿然躍入如此明顯的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利身為戰術家的資質則會受人質疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利若能順利奪回人質
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是亞瑟斯伯的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥卿還真分到了個苦差事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的意思是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟若失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥也會受牽連
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功勞也會歸到伊德里斯卿頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}艾賓格王國 第二公主莉迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エルビング王国 第二王女リディア
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯卿還真恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這塊蛋糕很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,923)\fad(500,500)}芙蘭西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}フランシア
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但以女性為人質…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法認同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也算是人質啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾 你們也吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(605,855)\fad(500,500)}法爾密·泰坦尼亞子爵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(605,925)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}バルアミー・タイタニア子爵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天不怕地不怕的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人真能派上用場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 作為吸引方修利的誘餌再適合不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能成功吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下必能移居天城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人也會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑藉此功升為公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我問候伊德里斯閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:11:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(675,923)\fad(500,500)}貝魯提耶大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:11:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(675,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ベルティエ大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 修連什麼時候來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天嗎？後天嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是修連 是方修利 閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定會來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在多半正在醞釀計策
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真符合提督的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟斯伯爵若是知道 肯定會氣個半死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督就會惹人生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說得這麼難聽嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣一來 我也成了反泰坦尼亞的罪犯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒有這個自覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰本身還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但需要滿足幾個條件才能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還需要軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:12:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個星球上應該有不少流民
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去號召一下如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用錢所買的軍隊會為錢賣主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不適合本次作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是還有你的艦隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}亞朗·麥佛迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}アラン・マフディー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算讓自己的同伴上陣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 博士會同行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想見識真正的方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 既沒有船又沒有軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕有點困難
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能指望開始就湊齊所有棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窮人的戰鬥都是要就地取材的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還有船的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我叫船長來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和他談談
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:13:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上無城 遍地開花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游擊隊為什麼都這麼喜歡拽文呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回答 請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是自由艾曼塔軍…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是李長遷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從桶的數量看來 還是不太夠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦倫科夫 能麻煩你陪船長去進貨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越多越好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大艦隊是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢找米蘭達…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？米蘭達？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她剛才就出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是帳單有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船的整備費
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看這個金額
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰能付得起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是獅子大開口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是趁火打劫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整備完成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:13:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若不付錢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若賴了這筆帳直接逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說破壞這間工廠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要強行起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船體也不會沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能想點辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有錢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這件事可沒法強求
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 辦法還是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 需要一個合適的冤大頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我去問問博士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有合適人選
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽過有關你的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:15:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這兩天連戰連勝嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長才是鋒頭正勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近期就要建一座大樓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羨煞旁人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我把樓錢掙回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 換兩張
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三張
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利地引蛇出洞了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧博士面子大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就看麥佛迪的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窩牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順子居然會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真走運
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來社長今天手氣好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我還不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 就是這份志氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是輸著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.53,0:16:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不是普通地壞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意讓對方先贏兩局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事能做到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他出老千
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打火機？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙應該不抽煙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到他居然還留有那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:16:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作弊成功率100%
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是泰坦尼亞和星際都市聯盟聯手抵制的神器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個惡黨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 我都快高興暈了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 足夠建兩三座大樓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 我可不能就這樣回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如再玩一局就收手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這麼決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭全額
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不換牌 不亮牌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這賭得還真是驚心動魄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我是不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎 小心輸個精光哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我已經當慣窮人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫大忙了 麥佛迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上說得好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡肯定當我是惡黨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.87,0:18:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個社長也真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那位也不是什麼好人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 不能多稱讚我兩句嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然 您就是天神下凡 老千之王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麥佛迪大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整備費都付清了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時可以起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我起碼掙了十倍的整備費
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就萬事俱備了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就盡早啟程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 巴傑斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜託你辦點事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能散佈些假情報
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利打算襲擊亞瑟斯府
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想盡快召集大量兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了救回心愛的女人 我不惜一切代價
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:19:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 讓我出多少錢都行 請助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利那傢伙已經上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據情報顯示 他聚集了大量兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟斯艦隊已盡數在艾曼塔集結
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他帶一整支艦隊過來 也是有來無回
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要大意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下官謹記在心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此計一成 你在泰坦尼亞就能飛黃騰達了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 請靜候佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督要的貨已經裝上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還預先留有餘裕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的船也準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開這裡20小時後會合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工錢也準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是別人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報操作也很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:19:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我順便拜託了李博士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和離開這裡的船全都打過招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一情報馬上就會滿宇宙飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直像煙火一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家賓館已經沒人收購了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:20:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現方修利艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長距離雷達顯示
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他衝這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓全艦立即出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能請您將艦隊指揮權交給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下官會封鎖全部航路 布下天羅地網
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是原艾里亞軍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.24,0:21:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓昔日的同伴自相殘殺也蠻有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮權就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您放心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}戰艦極光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}戦艦オーロラ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周邊航路 封鎖完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.33,0:22:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利艦隊 行進速度不變
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.28,0:22:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯然是衝著艾曼塔去的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 盯緊點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.78,0:22:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來 方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.35,0:24:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.46,0:24:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不能不去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.17,0:24:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 一定要把莉拉救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.31,0:24:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我 莉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.02,0:24:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(638,290)\fad(500,0)\fs90\bord5}潛入艾曼塔


